Error: [38;5;232mClient error: (403) PERMISSION_DENIED
* Client does not have sufficient permission. This can happen because the OAuth token does not have the right scopes, the client
  doesn't have permission, or the API has not been enabled for the client project.
* Request had insufficient authentication scopes.[39m
[90mRun `rlang::last_error()` to see where the error occurred.[39m
